[normal]·
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal] 
[normal]How effectively do local bodie
[normal]s work with each other and with Government departments and national transport agencies?
[normal]No knowledge of this.
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]Funding streams for cycling projects are more diverse than ever and are acquired and managed by different bodies. Opportunities have been missed where combining money from different funding streams (such as the Highways Agency, National Park, county and bo
[normal]rough councils) could have delivered greater benefits.  
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]&#xa0;
